# Simple colorized logger

Current version is: ‘v1.1.41’

To install use:

pip3 install –upgrade sclogger

Find docs in the [docs](/docs) folder.

Find code examples in the [examples](/docs/examples) folder.

<h2>Print example</h2>

![](/docs/images/sclogger.png)
